comment: This number is the inverse of the Pisot number at A293506.

mathematica: RealDigits[ Solve[1 - x - x^3 - x^5 == 0, x][[1, 1, 2]], 10, 111][[1]] (* _Robert G. Wilson v_, Oct 12 2017 *)
program: (PARI) solve(x = 0.6, 0.7, 1 - x - x^3 - x^5) \\ (Set precision high enough) _David A. Corneth_, Oct 12 2017
(PARI) { default(realprecision, 20080); x=solve(x=0.6, 0.7, 1 - x - x^3 - x^5)*10; for (n=0, 20000, d=floor(x); x=(x-d)*10; write("b293560.txt", n, " ", d)); } \\ _Iain Fox_, Oct 27 2017
